        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 29 at 5:27PM MDT until August 29 at 5:45PM MDT by NWS Goodland KS</headline>
        <description>At 527 PM MDT/627 PM CDT/, a severe thunderstorm was located 13 miles
north of Brewster, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Brewster.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
